rows.label: qst200419_0010
rows.name: Gahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200419_0020
rows.name:
Nice one, Vasara! I can see that you
move just like you did back then.

rows.label: qst200419_0030
rows.name:
I take back what I said. You have
not changed in the slightest.

rows.label: qst200419_0040
rows.name: It's just like that time...

rows.label: qst200419_0050
rows.name:
That time you disobeyed me,
betrayed your friends, and tried
to leave the Bloody Lobsters...

rows.label: qst200419_0060
rows.name: Gahahahah!

rows.label: qst200419_0070
rows.name: ...I don't see what's funny.

rows.label: qst200419_0080
rows.name:
You don't? But it's exhilarating!
The excitement of it!

rows.label: qst200419_0090
rows.name:
To think we might kill each
other again... It thrills
me like nothing else!

rows.label: qst200419_0100
rows.name: ...I thought I told you.

rows.label: qst200419_0110
rows.name: I have no recollection of you at all.

rows.label: qst200419_0120
rows.name:
You won't play along,
huh? Well, I don't mind.

rows.label: qst200419_0130
rows.name:
The generous guy that I
am, I will bury you with
my own hands once more!

rows.label: qst200419_0140
rows.name: Just like I did 20 years ago! Gahahaha!

rows.label: qst200419_0150
rows.name:
Foolish. Under the circumstances,
you have no hope of winning.

rows.label: qst200419_0160
rows.name: Huh? Oh, you're relying on friends now?

rows.label: qst200419_0170
rows.name: You, Vasara? Really?

rows.label: qst200419_0180
rows.name:
Ehehe... Well, certainly I would have
preferred to assassinate you...

rows.label: qst200419_0190
rows.name:
and with this crowd here, it'd
hardly be a proper assassination.

rows.label: qst200419_0200
rows.name:
Oh, I suppose I could just
wipe out the lot of them too
just like you would...

rows.label: qst200419_0210
rows.name: There, problem solved!
